item.title: The Basketcase
item.dc:creator: Sarah Cosper
item.description:
I’m all for a good makeover montage, (Helloooo Tai!), but Allison Reynolds looked way cooler with all that “black shit” under her eyes than she did after Claire got ahold of her. That headband was heinous. However… Claire’s lipsticked mouth is a thing of beauty forever and ever, amen.

The post The Basketcase appeared first on The Lab Bunny.
